snippet.title: Society for Scientific Exploration
snippet.description:
Since 1982, the Society for Scientific Exploration (SSE) has provided a critical forum for sharing original research into cutting edge and unconventional areas. Subjects often cross mainstream boundaries, yet may have profound implications for human knowledge and technology.  The SSE publishes an open access peer-reviewed Journal of Scientific Exploration, the popular EdgeScience magazine, makes its convention videos freely available here at YouTube. 

If you would like to take your support of our 501(c)(3) nonprofit a step further by networking with scientists and scholars at meetings and events, consider becoming an SSE member: https://www.scientificexploration.org/join

Views and opinions expressed in these videos belong only to the speakers, and are not necessarily endorsed by the SSE.
